Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:27.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,OFF THE COAST OF DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:31.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE THOUSAND SUNNY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky-{\i1}san{\i0} will be pissed if he sees this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The door got deformed, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she a Devil Fruit eater?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what kind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"BAD TASTE" Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy, oh boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like people who \Nhave no artistic sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just call me a mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa, who do you \Nthink you're talking to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Giolla-{\i1}sama{\i0} of \Nthe Don Quixote Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:30.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,GIOLLA\NTHE DON QUIXOTE FAMILY\N(THE TRÃ‰BOL ARMY)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Don Quixote Family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul is swinging!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see an image! My mind is gonna erupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna explode!\NAn image of liberty and beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got all flattened and smooth!\NHow dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's art. A work of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you ordinary people \Ncan't understand art.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the art crap! Turn us back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, turn us back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I can turn you back if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in exchange, you need to hand Momonosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nover to us without any trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Momo-{\i1}chan{\i0}!\NWe won't let them take you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my soul is swinging!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make you more beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get distorted anymore,\Nwhat will we look like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There is a hatch!\N--Should we go after them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy, oh boy! What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There they are!\N--When did they get out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you think you're doing?!\NGet back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll make you look more like art pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't reach us with your \Nbizarre power ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy, oh boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's getting mad, just as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, if she keeps using that weird power,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe Sunny will get all messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Franky-{\i1}san{\i0} will be furious\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but aside from that, can \Nwe even turn it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The room that used to be \Nthe men's dormitory...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all we can do now is\Ntry to keep it from getting
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,any more screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she focuses out this way!
