Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo's submarine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so that's how they got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They came hiding in the fog, didn't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize there were so many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?!\NThey're going to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go and take Momonosuke away\Nfrom them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Giolla-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul is swinging! I see an image!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is gonna erupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's gonna do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?! We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to aim at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother with the ship! We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's gonna explode!\NAn image of liberty and beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world should be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did it! We're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what beauty is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?\NIsn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! You can't call it a ship anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy, oh boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna fall for your trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0} ordered \Nme to kidnap Momonosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hijack your ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there is no way for you Straw Hats\Nto escape from Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our plan failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up and surrender yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any medical attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ricky! We can't just let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our job is to take care of all competitors\Nincluding treatment of injuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,especially you guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let people kill each other \Nin front of an audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NCut the treatment crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bleeding from the head!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take off your mask and let us take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch my mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you alright, Mr. Ricky?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're not allowed to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, hold him down.\NHe's badly wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to get treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move! I can walk by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go straight and take the \Nstairs to the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rebecca... I'm sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:29.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A WAITING ROOM FOR THE DON \NQUIXOTE FAMILY IN THE COLOSSEUM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat is fighting in \Nthe match now, Diamante.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the match is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker wants me to kill Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy's too indulgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's giving the man who couldn't \Nwin the match one more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy, Bellamy?\NAssassination is an easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish it up before the competition's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bellamy! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you'll get promoted\Nto be an executive of the Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're trying \Nto kill Lucy, Cavendish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Bartolomeo, aren't you?\NCongrats on making it to final.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Lucy, it's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not yours to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You want to kill him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's in the limelight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the one who will kill him.\NI won't let anybody else to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you're no exception!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get in my way, you'll get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My connection with him is much deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many people are eliminated already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle for Block C is heating up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so fierce both \Noffensively and defensively!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even though they're all tough fighters,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is one giant warrior who is\Nliterally sticking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a warrior of the new generation\Nfrom the famous Giants' country - Elbaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most formidable "Pirate Mercenary"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NHis name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hajrudin!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gigantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too big, you bastard!\NThat's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever seen a Giant \Nwho ate a Logia fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'll become once \NI win the Flare-Flare Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the king of...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all Giants!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just a single blow! \NIt was like lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can stop him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is a fighting bull \Nrunning out of control
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nshowing no fear for all those tough contenders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a killer bull who slayed \N21 death row prisoners
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nduring a fight in this very Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colosseum's Grim Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NBecause of his behavior, people call him Brutal Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And somehow, someone knows how to tame\Nand ride this Grim Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bursting into prominence, \Nwith his cool strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nhe instantly became a crowd favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go Usy (bull)!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that guy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyats-{\i1}san{\i0}, you should be impartial!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy! Go, go!\NTake them all down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He became popular even under \Na fake name! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a funny guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go Ucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, they're challenging Hajrudin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! Run, Ucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a disappointment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was obviously a mismatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rookie from Elbaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...crushed the Colosseum's Grim Reaper\Nand the unknown gladiator - Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyats-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Giant's been knocked down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:18.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
